{"tid":442053,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"眾多排名中某一個 QS 亞洲大學排名將科大排第一","createTime":"2017-10-20T09:05:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T12:00:23.000Z","uid":28614,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4ead95e3572c3fd618318d2d10ca90d92fe567c0","tid":442053,"uid":28614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T09:05:57.000Z","msg":"2013 年都排過一次 QS 亞洲排名第一，之後果年就即刻跌返落第五<br />\n同年 QS 世界排名科大都只係第二，更加唔洗講 Times 或者 US News 果啲排名<br />\n<br />\n點知返學見到啲同學打哂丁，上連登又講咩一大一大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感覺好似少少甜頭已經射到出血，麻煩各位同學謙虛少少，我地只係其中一個排名既其中一個分支榜高過港大 1 分咋，而且個 1 分係教授出 Paper 拎返黎，我地學生要繼續努力"},{"pid":"fcd2a022ea8fbb677f9c752afee3b9ff951d10ee","tid":442053,"uid":13816,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T09:19:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"97928f0fa773df5481e1248e2eda2af441de9fba","tid":442053,"uid":28614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T10:00:51.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"fa1e2ad7c348ad254d7f5f006df1ff746a2f2a10","tid":442053,"uid":28614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T10:46:38.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"1d89a4e4ccf8a79e4d02a30f788d7b2ad50fece7","tid":442053,"uid":134969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T10:50:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"740e9272493d897c2841b612e32da152b4920c1e","tid":442053,"uid":150611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T12:00:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}